EDUCATIONAL / PROOF-OF-CONCEPT — PUBLIC

Copyright (c) 2026 ryanGTR

This repository is a PUBLIC, educational proof-of-concept (PoC). It models a
bank's internal developer platform (IDP) for learning and demonstration
purposes only. It is NOT a production system.

- It contains NO real production data.
- It contains NO real credentials. All example values are clearly fake
  (e.g. EXAMPLE_FAKE_KEY_DO_NOT_USE) and exist solely to exercise the
  secret-scanning guardrail.
- The "internal / confidential" framing in the documents is part of the
  modelled scenario, NOT a real confidentiality classification.

Permission is hereby granted, free of charge, to any person obtaining a copy
of this repository, to use, copy, modify, and learn from it. Provided "as is",
without warranty of any kind, express or implied.
